            <div class="title">
                Liberated Europe (British Intervention)
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1944-12-08/debates/e8747562-c4b2-45f4-90f2-fbba1f86f135/Black-OutRegulations" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
