    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">The hon. Member is omitting to point out that these security people were also to be disarmed.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-1ccc144d-3d89-43d2-8ab9-a9c26603d019" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
