            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-db75facd-d1fc-40dc-b3b4-e7fd584c33e6" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
