            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-e497d3ef-836b-4a9e-bc6a-4d53fa34f5c3" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
