<p class="">On a point of Order, Mr. Speaker. In view of the fact that every Member of the House is conscious that the Prime Minister made that statement, is it clear that there will be no interference with HANSARD?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
